<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說現存的幾乎所有生物，<delay20 />
都是在這房間展示的化石還實際活著的時代<delay8 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一口氣大量出現的呢。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能實際看見並感受到<delay8 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牠們數億年前活著的樣子，<delay20 />
還真浪漫啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />牠們到底是<delay8 />
怎麼被封進土裡的啊？<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一直很想知道哩<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定是<delay8 />發生了什麼大事，<delay8 />
憑牠們的幹勁也走避不及吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得<delay8 />挺讓人難過的啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />展示在這房間裡的化石，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像是地球表面還幾乎是海水時
存在的生物呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我實在很難想像，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是我們的祖先<delay8 />
該不會<delay8 />也在這房間裡吧？</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算變成了化石，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />恐龍就是有魄力，<delay8 />真棒耶！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是能看到<delay8 />活生生的恐龍，<delay20 />
到底會是什麼感覺啊？<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是想像，<delay8 />就覺得好興奮啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡展示的<delay8 />恐龍化石<delay20 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一到了晚上，<delay8 />好像就會悄悄動起來喔！？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說不定還會<delay8 />跑去你家呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說笑的啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剛剛說的是玩笑話啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是可以見到<delay8 />真正的恐龍，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得我想要<delay8 />
拜託牠收我為徒啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為我小時候<delay20 />在圖鑑上看過恐龍，<delay8 />
覺得牠實在好帥啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我長久以來<delay8 />都一直很崇拜牠喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />我總覺得<delay8 />雖然牠的大小可以想像，<delay20 />
但身體的顏色<delay8 />就未必會跟圖鑑一樣了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />萬一是花朵圖案，<delay8 />那怎麼辦啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到陳列在這裡的這些生物<delay8 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以前其實都很稀鬆平常地生活著，<delay20 />
就讓我感慨萬分啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像這樣看著展覽，<delay8 />就讓我重新體認到，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也要把握眼前的時刻，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好好活在當下啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然陳列在這房間裡的，<delay8 />
都是數千萬年前的生物，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是化石當中，也有比較近代的吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />搞不好<delay20 />我們這個時代的生物，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有一天也會變成化石喔！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />還要很久以後就是了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖說大家都覺得<delay8 />化石有種浪漫啦，<delay20 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但從牠們緊張的僵硬模樣看來，<delay20 />
變成化石應該<delay8 />超讓人驚恐吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />變成了化石以後，
牠們依然以展覽品的形式<delay8 />大為活躍，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還真是名副其實的硬骨頭啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="100_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />化石還真是<delay8 />百看不厭啊！<delay40 />
光是想像牠們的時代<delay8 />發生過什麼事，
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就覺得很興奮啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總有一天我也要達成我的夢想，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到處去不同的島，<delay8 />
參觀那邊的<colour id="1" />博物館<colour id="65535" />！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果是面對自己喜歡的化石，<delay20 />
不管站著看多久<delay8 />都沒問題啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay20 />要是一直猛盯著看，<delay8 />
化石說不定也會覺得害羞，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我平常<delay8 />都會克制我自己啦！</message>
	<message label="100_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然化石在鑑定前<delay8 />看起來就是普通的石頭，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過一旦像這樣<delay8 />整齊地陳列，<delay8 />
就覺得挺有看頭的呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="200_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有這麼氣派的<colour id="1" />博物館<colour id="65535" />在，<delay20 />
埋藏在那的化石之謎被解開的日子，
我想已經不遠了。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後漸漸地，<delay20 /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />圍繞著這座島的
謎團也隨之真相大白<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣還挺浪漫的對吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這真是一間用心建造的展覽室啊～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能從中感受到<colour id="3" />傅達<colour id="65535" />的熱情哩。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總有一天，<delay20 />這裡會擺滿<delay20 />
從島上挖掘出來的化石吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 />真是令人期待啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要來這裡，<delay8 />就能好好地參觀
各式各樣的化石，<delay8 />真是太棒啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來得時不時地來確認<delay8 />
有沒有增加新的化石呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是期待<colour id="1" />博物館<colour id="65535" />將來的發展啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>